This then (through the `APIWrappers` wrapper classes) will eventually call https://github.com/JetBrains/intellij-community/blob/6a50833d3cbdfc342e8fe16d954938b9f465fb2e/jps/jps-builders-6/src/org/jetbrains/jps/javac/JpsJavacFileManager.java#L665, which is then used to implement `javax.tools.JavaFileManager`&#39;s `getFileForOutput` and `getJavaFileForOutput`.

